ftpserver

I've created this project to share files over my local network. you can install it as a service using WinSW to run it seamlessly in the background.

Getting Started
To get you started you can simply clone the repository:

    git clone https://github.com/eloraa/videofy-player

and install the dependencies

    yarn

Prerequisites
You need git to clone the repository. You can get git from
http://git-scm.com/

A number of node.js tools is necessary to initialize and test the project. You must have node.js and its package manager (npm) installed. You can get them from http://nodejs.org/. The tools/modules used in this project are listed in package.json and include yarn.

Run the Application

    yarn start
